HEADWORD: Agazed
<hw>A*gazed"</hw> <pr>(⟦adot⟧*g⟦amac⟧zd")</pr>, <pos>p. p.</pos>
<ety>[Only in p. p.; another spelling for <ets>aghast</ets>.]</ety>
<def>Gazing with astonishment; amazed.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The whole army stood <qex>agazed</qex> on him.</q>
<rj><qau>Shak.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
